articles.title: Trump warns the EU and UK are in line for tariffs — but a U.S. deal with Britain might be on the cards - CNBC
articles.description: U.S. President Donald Trump said trade tariffs would be imposed on the European Union and U.K., but he signaled that a deal could be worked out with Britain.
